This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Include codes from http://snomed.info/sct where concept is-a 105590001 (Substance)
  • Include codes from http://snomed.info/sct where concept is-a 260787004 (Physical object)

name: SNOMEDCTSupplyItem
title: SNOMED CT Supply Item
description: This value set includes [SNOMED CT](http://snomed.info/sct) where concept is-a 105590001 (Substance (substance)) or  concept is-a 260787004 (Physical object)  and provided as an example value set.
